Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid once again delivered his advance notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this time, he claimed he would return the items stolen by another thief in the past to the original owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The items, three in total, were all related to Sakamoto Ryouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the original owner Mr. Tarumi and the appraiser Mr. Hanamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:19.05,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tarumi Shishihiko (58)\NRyouma Exhibition Organizer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:20.76,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hanamura Masanosuke (63)\NAppraiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:24.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Held a Ryouma exhibition in the Suzuki Grand Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ruby-adorned gunbelt was put on display, said to be received by Ryouma from Takasugi Shinsaku along with a pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And rumor has it that he was aiming to steal that gunbelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the pistol was among the items Kid promised to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Metal detecting gates were installed at the exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it still bothers me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we really catch Kid with this move?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like fog clearing up in a swoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see through both romance and cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A never-before-heard return of treasures...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is Kid's real intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the officer guarding the museum entrance, how's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have yet to observe any guests quickly turning tail after seeing the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any problems at the metal detectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There have been no guests with a pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the exhibition room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this time, there is no one resembling Kid on the premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is Kid really coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid's never failed to show up each time he's made an announcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:25.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How, come forth, Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, I swear I'll apprehend you once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They really made it look like the airport terminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention there are even three gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Uncle for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something still bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he deliberately wrote in his notice that he'd "bring the pistol and the other items"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course he should've been able to predict that things would turn out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, I still haven't figured out how he intends to use the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I don't get the meaning behind the last sentence of the notice, "I pledge to clean up once and for all."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was he merely trying to be clever by using Ryouma's words?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or is there something he truly intends to clean up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, we should go in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hallway behind the Ryouma exhibition entrance is blocked by a wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that one has to pass through the gates to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing between them are the restrooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But inside each restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is only one window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Metal bars are installed to prevent any entrance from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bringing a pistol inside thus seems impossible, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at all of the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attention, our valued quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The traffic in this room has become extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our sincere apologies, but we are imposing a viewing limit of ten minutes to the Ryouma exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no matter what he says, it doesn't seem like anyone plans on leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still two hours before the announced time, but Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} might already be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with the gates, he wouldn't be able to sneak the pistol in...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard he was coming here today to return things that another thief stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might just give up, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What other thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three items Kid's returning this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryouma's last letter, his blood-stained sake cup, and the pistol he had on him when he was assassinated...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:06:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were all stolen twenty years ago by the damsel thief, Phantom Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phantom Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was a great thief known as the Shouwa's Woman of Twenty Faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She used to deploy horror-inducing tricks and target only the rich and large corporations with unscrupulous earnings...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she was really popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, she loses to my Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why Would Kid come to return things that lady thief stole?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're both thieves after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to use the restroom again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it sure is crowded here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost like a bargain sale...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, who pushed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phantom Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phantom Lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems Phantom Lady really was the one who stole those three items 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for some reason she suddenly stopped all criminal activity afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, she still did send out advanced notices and leave evidence of forced entries after that, but nothing was found stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:28.98,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ryouma's Pistol\NSmith & Wesson Model 1 1/2\NFirst issue\NCaliber: .32\NAmmunition: Rimfire\NShots: 5\NLength: Approximately 17cm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, the Ryouma's pistol taken in her last heist was a .32 caliber, five shots...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About 17 centimeters in Length.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seventeen centimeters would be about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roughly this size?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,June 24th, 1867.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This pistol also appeared in Ryouma's letter addressed to his elder sister Otome on that date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Measuring six sun [7 inches] and chambering five shots, and while it way appear smaller than a dagger...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,," 'Tis a firearm capable of killing a man from a distance of fifty ken [100 yards] proximately."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door won't open...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, he shut it with a stopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how'd you get the gun in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you pass the gates?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remove the lead from the inside grip, I can pass right through!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It also becomes super light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, due to the sheer number, transporting them was tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lead from the grip?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheer number of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time I only came to return the stolen items.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get in the way, Great Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, will it really be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if Kid gets caught by the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us have faith in our elusive gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he makes his magnificent escape, we will once again make huge profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's coming to return those items!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to fret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've worked our plan all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to your finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was appraising a Japanese sword this morning and accidentally cut my finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he already in the exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you---
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was afraid you were going to get crushed in a crowd like this, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And by the looks of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll get even worse at the announced time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:10:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something on your right sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to be some writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Tetsu no hitotsu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"One piece of iron"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it some kind of code?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you bump into anything inside the exhibition?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone knocked me into the gunbelt display case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gunbelt display case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be he...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really intends to produce rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to clean up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This soiled exhibition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, that bastard Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where does he plan to get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even a slippery guy like him cannot pass through the metal detecting gates while carrying a pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd like to think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he managed to get through the gates, maybe the pistol he has is a counterfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I supposed that would have to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll have Sensei here examine the three items immediately upon their return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pray that they are indeed the genuine articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aside from that, is Ryouma's gunbelt all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although we did a final check on the display case before the museum opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about we head to the exhibition now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since if the three items he's returning turned out to be fake, and if the gunbelt were stolen on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be just too terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's now completely crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s announced time is in four more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think it's about time that we go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there are so many people that we wouldn't even see Kid if he showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Uncle Jirokichi too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let us through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be better if you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why shouldn't we go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't want to get wet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it seems Kid really is going to clean up in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, there are too many visitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't guard properly like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's standing on the gun belt case!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}, you're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got through the metal detecting gates so he's unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What "clean up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing that's getting cleaned up down to the bone is you, after your arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct, I'm cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in order to clean things up, I need water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, right now, in this very room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall create some rain for your viewing pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that guy up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bastard, he used the flame to set off the fire sprinklers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I shall take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going return those three items?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that, this shower shall make everything clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like how rain washes away the mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blasted guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He tampered with the sprinkler's water pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water mist is obscuring him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Freaking Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think he can escape by blending in with the quests?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did any guests leave through the gate just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two or three people did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go and detain the one who's wet among them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he changed into his disguise during the shower, he should be soaking wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's pouring outside as well, nearly all of the guests are soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the footprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Follow the damp footprints that lead away from the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, the floor's covered in damp frootprints too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why he was waiting for a rainy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what about the three items he said he'd return?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are placed here on top of the gunbelt's display case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I accidentally got my blood on the sake cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since all three items appear to be replicas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is whether this gunbelt is safe or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The anti-theft device was destroyed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, does it mean Kid switched the gunbelt inside with a fake!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He completely got you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What seems to be the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something dripping down from the case's description plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, it's double-layered...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stuck another plate with the same descriptions written in watercolors over the original...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that the writing underneath would appear when it got drenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this was because my sleeve was damp from the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The letters from the gunbelt description plate was thus reversed on your sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what's written on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"This gunbelt was a complete counterfeit from the start, because..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They assumed it would be stolen and manufactured a large number of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was essential was that the stolen items appear on the news and be made known to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:17:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, those who're responsible for the large number of forgeries sold them to wealthy Ryouma fans via a third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'd say that those items were stolen just a few days before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The advantage to this kind of operation is that nothing will be reported even if the buyers discover that the items are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since they attempted to secretly purchase stolen goods, they're in a bind and can't take the matter to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Phantom Lady's crimes went unnoticed after she stole those three items.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she only targeted those who bought the three items' forgeries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She then entrusted the mass of forgeries that she had gathered to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Lady then asked you to expose the dirty deeds of those two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, without the cooperation the exhibition organizer who knowingly displayed fakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the appraiser who certifies the forgeries as real, these crimes cannot be committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister Thief, or Would-be Ryouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is what it says on this plate true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all, where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The so-called "mass numbers of forgeries"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we only have a plastic pistol...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fake sake cup and a letter, these three items.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This gun belt and pistol were put around my waist without me knowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My waist too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"borrowed from Mr. Tarumi's warehouse," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn that Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took advantage of the crowd to put the belts on our waists!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You folks broke that anti-theft device in advance to make it look like a robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:19:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this time you planned to sell of the gunbelts, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it this time!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's also text where the paint came off of this other description plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It meticulously goes into detail about why this item is a forgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the last bit of text is in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In English?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:19.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,PULL...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pull... pull down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it telling me to pull down this hanging scroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryouma's letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there are many more copies of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:20:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appears that they are all the same letter as the one that was placed on the gunbelt case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a setup by Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I concur!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no evidence that we made or sold any of th---
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sonoko!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's written on Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It says "crash it"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey what are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a pethora of sake cups inside the vase!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more appears that each of them has blood on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we conduct a DNA test on the blood, it'll be clear who was making the phony sake cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless you plan to explain it away by rubbing your cut finger on them like earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you did was to get your blood on all of the cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure we'll find it when we search your warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mountain load of forged items that you haven't sold yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that you figured out I was Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't I look like an ordinary middle-aged guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though they were forged plastic pistols, they would get quite bulky if you must carry a lot of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the more so when combined with the letters and sake cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I searched through the crowd for someone with a disproportionately skinny lower body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that would be you who were pretending to be fat in order to hide so many items on your person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you won't show signs of sweating because you're in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:23:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I stuck one of these button transmitters on that skinny ankle of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.45,0:23:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when my pursuit glasses caught your position, I called out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you turning me over to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll let you got this time for Ryouma's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you a Ryouma fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My motheris.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She once played the role of Ryouma's elder sister Otome, so she's gone gaga over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, she got rave reviews for being to cute to play Otome...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her popularity soared because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Consider us both to be unable to stand up to our mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We're the same"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me that Phantom Lady is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,*Hey, hey, isn't that Miyasaka Yuuya over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,*You know, he's the one who was on the news last year after being charged with injury to others due to inebriation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.77,0:24:07.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.17,0:24:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He beat me up again...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.28,0:24:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miyasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.53,0:24:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,DEAD!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.44,0:24:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.66,0:24:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something wasn't right.
